 Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aJewish scholarszRussiavBiography. 0aJewszRussiaxHistoryy19th century. 0aJewszRussiaxHistoryy20th century. 0aJewszRussiaxIntellectual lifey19th century. 0aJewszRussiaxIntellectual lifey20th century. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Jewish Studies.2bisacsh1 aBrumfield, William Craft.1 aCraft Brumfield, William, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161811557740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781618115577423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781618115577.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK